components.name: GitHub Packages
components.description: GitHub Packages is a software package hosting service on GitHub. It allows you to host your software packages privately or publicly and use packages as dependencies in your projects. If GitHub experiences a service interruption to Packages, this could impact the dependencies you count on in your CircleCI builds. If this component is marked anything other than Operational, more information can be found at: https://www.githubstatus.com/

We have implemented a fix and are still working to asses impact
Job details are not available in the UI. We are investigating the cause and severity of the impact.

scheduled_maintenances.name: Brownout: preparing to sunset MacOS intel resources.

incident_updates.body:
We are conducting brownouts for the following macOS resource class on June 20, 2024 in preparation for EOL on June 28, 2024.
Gen2 macos.x86.medium.gen2
For more information on this brownout and sunsetting macOS Intel resources, see the discuss post. https://discuss.circleci.com/t/macos-intel-support-deprecation-in-january-2024/48718
